reviews.reviewText: Love this frame! It is just as pictured! Nice quality frame; the mat is also of nice quality! I am very pleased! Can't believe what I paid for it! Thank you Walmart and thank you for securing it very well! The effort put in packing it so securely so that they would not get damaged is very much appreciated and does display consideration and respect for your customers!
